      "content": "yeah i looked at the cron jobs and they aren't running during these windows. it just feels like there's something invisible killing the requests. like it's almost as if something is just jumping in and breaking things in the middle of the logic flow. do you think it could be something at the network or infra level that we aren't seeing in the application logs?",
